Invocation Name: rock thirty radio
des: Rock 30 Radio is an extension of the LA Lloyd Rock 30 Countdown. You'll hear archived shows of the Rock 30 and the remainder of the schedule features Today's Rock artist's songs mixed with hits from 2020-2021. You'll also hear Podcast interviews with many of the artists who have co-hosted the Rock 30.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
